Text: Few know the whole story. From what I recall, begins something like this, before
  history began, Palestine was the cradle of civilization, a paradise for the humanity,
  a kingdom of happiness, so all the humanity became greedy to squat this land, they
  fight each other and create ages of war to live there. A land of heaven lure the
  gods who created this land to live there, but it was impossible and confused ...etc
